name: Rock Paardestaart - Heknie
description:
Synth freaks curiously check out each other's synth collection, and nervously ponder: 
Is I the OG? Or is it he?
An often heard question in such investigations is: do you own a 303? Or an 808?
Referring to the iconic Roland TB 303 – the box that produces the epic roaring and grinding acid sounds and to the Roland TR 808 - the holy grail of vintage drum machines used in very very many techno, electro and house tracks.

This poem by Rock Paardestaart refers to an excerpt of such dialogues.
